{"tid":1372714,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"紐卡素班主艾殊利指責賓尼迪斯為錢離開球會執教中超","createTime":"2019-07-27T13:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T04:04:38.000Z","uid":14075,"like":2,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0b5cd96d3d9c101908404c271ddc03eb05b7f002","tid":1372714,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:28:04.000Z","msg":"Newcastle owner Mike Ashley claims it was impossible to keep Rafael Benitez at St James&rsquo; Park &ndash; <span style=\"color: red;\">because the former Magpies boss was only motivated by money.<br />\n</span><br />\nHe told the Daily Mail: &ldquo;If you come out and say the things he did you would think it was football club first, Rafa second, money third. I&rsquo;d say it was money first, Rafa, then the club last. He took the totally soft option, took the money and went to China.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">That disappoints me</span>. If he&rsquo;d gone back to Real Madrid, or a top six club in the Premier League, I get it. But it was about money and all he had to do was say that from the beginning.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;My view always was we had to keep Rafa. For my own personal safety we had to keep Rafa. I thought he had us offside, he had us cornered, it wasn&rsquo;t fair, it wasn&rsquo;t right, I&rsquo;ve been totally out-manoeuvred, I probably shouldn&rsquo;t own a football club, it&rsquo;s ridiculous, but I&rsquo;m a big boy.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;At one stage they were talking about a one-year extension and I said my preference would be for an eight-year contract. That&rsquo;s what I have to do in business when I invest. I have to take a medium to long-term view. I don&rsquo;t worry about my takings on a Saturday.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Looking back, though, it doesn&rsquo;t really matter what Rafa asked for because I think the Chinese thing was done. He had talked about what he could earn in China previously. We were not even slightly surprised by that move.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"d56c8d521b63fcce2b6dd93471de8eb0da0ae9b6","tid":1372714,"uid":173852,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:46:16.000Z","msg":"佢係咪賤撚到咁"},{"pid":"2afd5510f3c0a89acbaf3a52b7766df33d3721f4","tid":1372714,"uid":8636,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:18:58.000Z","msg":"咁你又為咩炒古迪亞里斯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26489e05bc17381cfb90d2958187fd150d466c48","tid":1372714,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:25:10.000Z","msg":"呢條死肥佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a74555f607084b7f634bda07b981809476d2de","tid":1372714,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />li條垃圾 應該成個足球界無人會撐佢"},{"pid":"68569e04d90cf7ba9b111d391e82c78267165677","tid":1372714,"uid":75028,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:25:53.000Z","msg":"無恥程度好比何妖"},{"pid":"38088a0da72af886167012ab895eaadf94dcf97e","tid":1372714,"uid":12034,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:32:09.000Z","msg":"狃卡素又搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01053c468a42687aa969f5bf2dea080f56e6c8f0","tid":1372714,"uid":103947,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T20:03:43.000Z","msg":"我淨係知無左肥賓朗當艾約斯等降班啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3684efe9e0f02652ebf72bff0105555abaef13b0","tid":1372714,"uid":85284,"like":11,"dis